Official PyTorch implementation of the core algorithms from the paper: **"High-precision rolling force prediction for hot rolling based on multimodal physical information and reinforcement learning"**.

This repository provides an industrial-grade, closed-loop AI system designed for hot strip mill production. It uniquely integrates **Data-Driven Deep Learning**, **Mechanistic Physical Models**, **Reinforcement Learning (RL)**, and **Model Predictive Control (MPC)** to achieve unprecedented accuracy and robustness in complex industrial environments.

